data.description: Welcome to a fabulous townhome that is like new, move-in ready and waiting for its next owner! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home, built in 2020, offers a perfect blend of updates and comfort. As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by an inviting open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The home has natural light throughout, making the home feel inviting from the entrance. The kitchen features newer appliances, cabinet space, a closet pantry, and a stylish island that encourages both casual meals and entertainment. Upstairs, you'll discover a spacious primary with an ensuite bathroom and generously sized walk-in closet. The bathroom conveniently has two vanity sinks, perfect for morning routines. The two additional bedrooms have their own closets and access to a full bathroom, offering the option to have two extra bedrooms or to convert a room into an at home office.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite townhouse your new home. Schedule a viewing today!
